name: HolidayGiftWishes
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: holiday gift wishes
Developer Terms of Use
des: This skill allows Alexa to conduct a one-on-one interview. The interview topic is centered around your holiday wish list. The questions asked by Alexa are open-ended, with Alexa delivering follow-up questions based on the previous answer. You will always have the ability to say “Help” to get more information on how to answer the current question, or you can say “Repeat” to hear the question or options another time. Each time the skill is launched, the skill will immediately pick back up where the conversation left off in the current interview, or it will begin a new interview.
priv:
Developer Privacy Policy
The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
